            /- A literal translation of the paper would read:
                (1/n : в„қ) вҖў (E1 Оө2 n).toMat * ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.log.toMat - (Пғ'' n).M.log.toMat) вүӨ ((R1 ПҒ Оө).toReal + Оө2) вҖў (E1 Оө2 n).toMat
